data.description: Large 0.28 acre level lot on quiet street near lake with Hill Country Views. Per city, water and sewer lines on street. Beautiful Homes. Enjoy the incredible lake amenities with access to waterfront parks, boat ramps, parks, golf courses, gym, pool, fishing hole, and more! Close to Balcones Canyonland National Wildlife Refuge where you can enjoy hiking and wildlife. About 15 min to Cedar Park shopping / retail. No restrictions when to build, or who to build with.
